    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your talent for slaughter lets you dispatch helpless opponents before they can recover.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Dastardly Finish, sneak attack +5d6, studied target class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a standard action that does not provoke attacks of opportunity, you can attempt a coup de grace against a cowering, helpless, or stunned opponent that you have designated as your studied target.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 10 stamina points when you use this feat to increase your weapon's critical multiplier by 1 ( x2 becomes x3, and x3 becomes x4) for your coup de grace.",
